Echo Shaw Elementary School
April 14, 2019 at 7:59 AM ·

Congratulations to Oregon’s top Spanish Spellers! These students will represent Oregon at the national spelling bee, held in Denver, Colorado in July! Winners are (from left to right):
2nd place Cytlalie Najera, Neil Armstrong Middle School - Forest Grove School District;
1st place Solana Quiroz, Alder Creek Middle School - North Clackamas School District;
3rd place Yisel Rodriguez Luna, Meadow Park Middle School - Beaverton School District.

Felicidades a los ganadores del concurso de deletreo en español. Estos estudiantes representarán al estado de Oregon en el concurso nacional que será en julio en Denver, Colorado. Ganadores son (de izquierdo a derecho):
2o lugar Cytlalie Najera, Neil Armstrong Middle School - Forest Grove School District;
1er lugar Solana Quiroz, Alder Creek Middle School - North Clackamas School District;
3er lugar Yisel Rodriguez Luna, Meadow Park Middle School - Beaverton School District.

